üß™ LAB PART (VERY IMPORTANT FOR VIVA + CCEE)
üîπ LAB 1: Create Digital Signature using XCA
Steps:
Open XCA
Create New Database
Generate Private Key
Create Certificate (Self-signed or CA-signed)
Export certificate (if required)
üîπ LAB 2: Digitally Sign a Word Document
Open Word ‚Üí File ‚Üí Info
Select Protect Document
Choose Add a Digital Signature
Select certificate created in XCA
Sign document
‚úî Any modification ‚Üí signature invalid

üîπ LAB 3: Digitally Sign a PDF Document
Open PDF in Adobe Reader
Tools ‚Üí Certificates ‚Üí Digitally Sign
Select area ‚Üí choose certificate
Save signed PDF
‚úî Integrity + non-repudiation ensured

üéØ CCEE QUICK REVISION (SESSION 9)
Aadhaar e-Sign = legally valid
Uses OTP/Biometrics
No physical token required
Time stamping = proof of time
XCA = certificate management tool
Document change ‚Üí signature invalid
